Class ConsumptionModel

java.lang.Object
  eu.cassandra.sim.entities.Entity
      eu.cassandra.sim.entities.appliances.ConsumptionModel

public class ConsumptionModel
extends Entity

Class for storing the variables of a consumption model. It has no functionality except parsing a JSON string and return the values on demand.
